•
This weekend the Shop employees challenged the Innetech crew to a special Game of Skate tournament in the Pro Course.
—
The rules were simple; 
• 2 skaters from each crew 
• 3 games of skate 
 - One game on Flat
 - Two games on Pro Course obstacles 
—
With bragging rights (and lunch) on the line the two squads battled it out for SPoT supremacy...who did you have ur money on??!
—
Teams
Innetech: @rolo.c & @marsefarmer_ 
Shop Guys: @timgasiorski & @skatestoppers_ 
—
📱: @bowser_media_lab 
#SPoTSkateBattle #SPoTTeam #SPoTTampa

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Skatepark of Tampa on August 12, 2021 tagging @adidasskateboarding. May be an image of smoking and toecap shoes.

node.text:
With inspiration drawn from the '90s, the Gazelle shoes from @adidasskateboarding are reimagined as a Skate Shoe legend. With ADITUFF™ technology and durable soles, these shoes were built to take the abuse. Suede upper and a vulcanized outsole. 💥💥

Now available in the victory crimson/footwear white/bluebird colorway 🏆🏆

#adidasskateboarding #gazelleadv #SPoTTampa
